Title: Internalization and the MNE: a note on the spread of ideas
Pages: 116-124
Author-Name: A Edward Safarian
Author-Workplace-Name: Joseph L Rotman School of Management, University of Toronto, Ontario, Canada
File-URL: http://www.palgrave-journals.com/jibs/journal/v34/n2/pdf/8400011a.pdf
