Author-Name: Witold J Henisz
Author-Workplace-Name: The Wharton School, University of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia, PA, USA
File-URL: http://www.palgrave-journals.com/jibs/journal/v34/n2/pdf/8400015a.pdf
