Title: Experience, imitation, and the sequence of foreign entry: wholly owned and joint-venture manufacturing by South Korean firms and business groups in China, 1987&ndash;1995
Pages: 185-198
Author-Name: Mauro F Guill&eacute;n
Author-Workplace-Name:  [1] The Wharton School &amp; Department of Sociology, University of Pennsylvania, Philadelphia, PA, USA [2] Instituto de Empresa, Madrid, Spain
